# Jarvis AI Assistant - Environment Variables Configuration

# ============================================
# OpenAI API (Required for AI responses)
# ============================================
EXPO_PUBLIC_OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key_here

# ============================================
# ElevenLabs API (Required for voice synthesis)
# ============================================
EXPO_PUBLIC_ELEVENLABS_API_KEY=your_elevenlabs_api_key_here

# ============================================
# Google Custom Search API (Optional - for web search)
# Get from: https://console.cloud.google.com
# ============================================
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SEARCH_API_KEY=your_google_search_api_key_here
EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_SEARCH_ENGINE_ID=your_google_search_engine_id_here

# ============================================
# OpenWeatherMap API (Optional - for weather)
# Get from: https://openweathermap.org/api
# ============================================
EXPO_PUBLIC_OPENWEATHER_API_KEY=your_openweather_api_key_here

# ============================================
# NewsAPI (Optional - for news headlines)
# Get from: https://newsapi.org
# ============================================
EXPO_PUBLIC_NEWS_API_KEY=your_newsapi_key_here

# ============================================
# Instructions for obtaining API keys
# ============================================

# 1. OpenAI API Key:
#    - Visit: https://platform.openai.com/api-keys
#    - Create a new API key
#    - Copy and paste here

# 2. ElevenLabs API Key:
#    - Visit: https://elevenlabs.io/app/api-keys
#    - Sign up or log in
#    - Copy your API key

# 3. Google Custom Search:
#    - Visit: https://console.cloud.google.com
#    - Create a new project
#    - Enable Custom Search API
#    - Create credentials (API key)
#    - Visit: https://cse.google.com/cse/
#    - Create a search engine and get the engine ID

# 4. OpenWeatherMap API:
#    - Visit: https://openweathermap.org/api
#    - Sign up for free account
#    - Get API key from API keys section

# 5. NewsAPI:
#    - Visit: https://newsapi.org
#    - Sign up for free account
#    - Get API key from dashboard

# ============================================
# Important Notes
# ============================================
# - Never commit this file with actual keys to version control
# - Keep your API keys secure and private
# - Rotate keys periodically
# - Monitor API usage to avoid unexpected charges
# - Use environment variables in production
